{"tid":471384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫敗陣 ViuTV擸晒金像金馬香港獨家播映權","createTime":"2017-11-17T07:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T13:39:31.000Z","uid":37554,"like":487,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"3abd8928e543ad36e861d968679a2f0c49e7b564","tid":471384,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"第37香港電影金像獎將於明年4月15日舉行，過往金像獎直播，唔係無綫就係亞視，而自從2012年第32屆開始，香港獨家播映權一直落喺無綫手上。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據《蘋果》收到可靠消息，ViuTV嚟緊喺無綫手上搶到第37金像獎香港免費電視獨家播映權，但到時會唔會中間唔加插廣告，一切仲要等開會先決定點做。本報記者致電ViuTV製作部副總裁金廣誠求證，他稱：「有消息嘅話我哋會公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n金像獎播映權每年都會公開投標，除價高者得之外，仲要睇埋標書嘅其他條件，先決定到邊間機構可以中標。因為金像獎係有政府公帑贊助，所以規定要有Free To Air嘅電視台。據知，今年金像獎方便原定邀請本港3間免費電視台ViuTv、無綫同奇妙電視入標。不過奇妙電視仍未開台，所以今年只有兩間免費電視台申請播映權。<br />\n<br />\nViuTV其實舊年已經想攞金像獎嘅免費電視獨家播映權，但因為佢哋舊年4月先至開台，個台太新，所以直播權最終輸咗俾無綫，直至嚟緊一屆終於爭贏。<br />\n另外，本月25號舉行嘅第54屆金馬獎，ViuTV亦攞到香港免費電視播映權，同now TV嘅收費頻道衛視電影台一齊直播。<br />\n<br />\n金像獎尚未公佈入圍名單，不過估計《空手道》、《29+1》、《拆彈專家》、《追龍》同《狂獸》都應該有份角逐。"},{"pid":"2ae02cc0ca8163ab3a450f97926f247d407f8333","tid":471384,"uid":22858,"like":48,"dislike":8,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌柒CCTVB <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、民國復興、群龍共舞、優美開始、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、JR、RedBaron (Epiphany)、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4046dab4ba7419fedc222352e55dc6db19e3dc7a","tid":471384,"uid":45213,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"好波呀Richard"},{"pid":"81cc5efae91bb4e9e3aac053bcf4182b9e1c3c44","tid":471384,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"TVB限奶 仲播"},{"pid":"30e6a35d92dc1270a53aabadea614549c51871c5","tid":471384,"uid":99642,"like":6,"dislike":31,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"Tvb唔稀罕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ed6016450e0361172e11e8487fa3f75141d06a","tid":471384,"uid":107472,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"都無人睇嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc1c5e354cc36c8e11cfee7f71f8980e3c5db51","tid":471384,"uid":3180,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"Cctvb咁鍾意cut「政治不正確」得獎者感想丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無撚得俾你地cut喇"},{"pid":"0e7d29d119cef0ee08c720d22d1867b7af2c99f5","tid":471384,"uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都無人睇嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金像無人睇, 港產片無咩人睇 (除左王晶電影之外.... 《追龍》票房都遠勝《空手道》)<br />\n<br />\n但CCTVB依然大把人睇"},{"pid":"4d358efe6447c6e6aabf7f82b11d910a3b4e82bb","tid":471384,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nviutv好波, 希望原汁原味, 一字不cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c022450ea84a05cf3ebf556baa2bac64fd36ec1c","tid":471384,"uid":77143,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都無人睇嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<